headline: REX Financial launches covered call Nvidia ETF hours before earnings release

Rhodium Group Director Reva Goujon comes on Yahoo Finance's Nvidia earnings special to speak further on the United States' export controls on AI semiconductors and Nvidia CEO Jensen Huang's relationship with President Trump. Also catch Benchmark Company's Cody Acree full interview with Yahoo Finance on Nvidia's business in China and whether it can overcome new trade barriers.
